title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 21 2022
description:
OutKick's Ian Miller, author of "Unmasked," joins Clay and Buck to discuss where we stand on covid. Pfizer CEO: We'll need a new covid shot every year. Biden asks for more covid money, says next pandemic is around the corner. Fauci calls for forever masking. Senator Josh Hawley joins C&B, blasts the Senate gun control bill, Biden's gas tax trick. Kids break into Florida mansion, get caught when they put videos on social media.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
